		}
		{
			description: ["Begin with the Framed Cube, then learn the small toolset instead of hand-crafting every variant. The saw selects shapes, the hammer and wrench adjust them, the screwdriver changes supported camo states, the blueprint copies completed frames, and the key preserves a chosen shape against neighbour updates."]
